  sdlmess-0.149.ebuild:
  add slot dep for repoman

  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> sdlmess-0.148_p1.ebuild,
  sdlmess-0.149.ebuild:
  Drop old Python implementations

  30 Jan 2015; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> sdlmess-0.148_p1.ebuild,
  sdlmess-0.149.ebuild:
  remove alsa use flag (bug #514600); use system portmidi lib; drop ppc until
  portmidi is keyworded

  15 May 2014; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> sdlmess-0.148_p1.ebuild,
  sdlmess-0.149.ebuild:
  Fix USE dependency on media-libs/libsdl, "audio" USE flag was renamed to
  "sound", bug 357661.

